message, like:

     cd /tmp/nix-build-f3slzg4g3h99yqcj6lzjwc1cvcdwg6dd-torcx.drv-0
     
     /nix/store/b48470bj4b8d4x6z5rr62924n30cwsiq-stdenv/setup: line 16: fail: command not found
